deliveryMessages: Or fastest delivery Wednesday, February 14. Order within 22 hrs 25 mins
features: 【Convenient Structure】The C-shaped design allows you to slide this small end table under a chair, sofa or other furniture, offer you convenient access to your laptop for home office. Ideal for adding an extra table lamp, eating a meal while watching TV, or serve as a desk in a pinch.

【Versatile Uses】The side table can be used as an end table, couch table, TV tray table, laptop table or nightstand and meets your needs for daily use. The top shelf provides convenient space for placing laptop, books, magazines, coffee, snacks, a meal or other items.

【Sturdy & Durable】With 4 height adjustable plastic feet, the slim couch table can be used on uneven floors or carpets. The triangular metal joints and extended bottom frame design increase the stability of the little table. Maximum load capacity up to 22 lbs.

【Extra Storage Pocket】Provides enough display and storage space. One large bag of 14.3"*9.5" for tablet, newspapers and magazines, four small cloth bags for temporary storage of remote control, mobile phone and charger without taking up too much room space.

【Fit Small Spaces】Sized at 16”L x 11.6”W x 28”H, easily fits the gaps between your couches or the tight spots beside your bed. For homes without more space for traditional nightstands and sofa side tables, this c table is certainly the excellent choice.

【Easy to Assemble & Move】Simple product construction, numbered parts and easy-to-follow instructions allow you to effortlessly assemble this sofa side table within 15 minutes with tools in the package. The lightweight design allow the snack table to be moved around.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great small space table
reviews.reviewText: It went together pretty easily with pretty clear diagram instructions (I am not gifted in this area and it took only 20 minutes and I didn’t have to re-do anything, so piece of cake for the mechanically inclined!) Extra screws included is thoughtful in case one rolled away or something. The fake wood looks good, with wood grain texture even. Hey no rings will ever mar it. The pouch thing is slim, room for only 1-2 magazines or files which is good (no piling up). Other little pouches good for phone, glasses, pens, password book sized stuff. Better than a shelf that could be bumped with wall mounted pouch under it that I’d overfill. A 4” slimmer top would have worked for me, preferable even, but this one is less wide than any others I saw. Price is right and came fast.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Vantic C Shaped End Table is what it is
reviews.reviewText: This small, inexpensive, side table certainly met expectations. It is a lightweight table that is tall enough to go over the arm of our sofa recliner. It was easy to assemble with clear instructions. It was not designed to be classic furniture and it's not. That said, with careful use it will meet our needs for years to come.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Watch it's weight tolerance.
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to stack three stereo components on it. They fit perfectly, but if I gave it a push, I was afraid that I could tip it over as it was top heavy. Yes, it could probable hold 60lbs, but I wouldn't recommend it, especially if you have kids or pets. I repurposed it for something else. I ordered another piece of furniture for the stereo stack. If you have a small lamp and an alarm clock radio at bedside, it should work fine.
